#: _versions/3.34/guides/websockets-next-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Both the <<server-api>> and <<client-api>> define _endpoints_ that are used to consume and send messages.\n"
"The endpoints are implemented as CDI beans and support injection.\n"
"Endpoints declare <<callback-methods,_callback methods_>> annotated with `@OnTextMessage`, `@OnBinaryMessage`, `@OnPingMessage`, `@OnPongMessage`, `@OnOpen`, `@OnClose` and `@OnError`.\n"
"These methods are used to handle various WebSocket events.\n"
"Typically, a method annotated with `@OnTextMessage` is called when the connected client sends a message to the server and vice versa."
msgstr "Tanto o ` <<server-api>> ` quanto o ` <<client-api>> ` definem _endpoints_ utilizados para receber e enviar mensagens. Os endpoints sĂŁo implementados como beans CDI e suportam injeĂ§ĂŁo. Os endpoints declaram xref:callback-methods[mĂŠtodos de callback] anotados com `@OnTextMessage` , `@OnBinaryMessage` , `@OnPingMessage` , `@OnPongMessage` , `@OnOpen` , `@OnClose` e `@OnError` . Esses mĂŠtodos sĂŁo utilizados para lidar com diversos eventos do WebSocket. Normalmente, um mĂŠtodo anotado com `@OnTextMessage` ĂŠ chamado quando o cliente conectado envia uma mensagem ao servidor e vice-versa."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/websockets-next-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The client API also includes <<client-connectors,connectors>> that are used to configure and create new WebSocket connections."
msgstr "A API do cliente tambĂŠm inclui xref:client-connectors[conectores] que sĂŁo utilizados para configurar e criar novas conexĂľes WebSocket."

